longBusinessSummary: Litium AB (publ) provides solutions for digital commerce through the litium commerce cloud platform in Sweden. The company's products comprise Lithium Ehandel, CMS, PIM, and accelerator, as well as other add-ons. Litium AB (publ) was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
